com.gnostice.pdfone
Class PdfPopUpAnnot

java.lang.Object
  com.gnostice.pdfone.PdfAnnot
      com.gnostice.pdfone.PdfPopUpAnnot
All Implemented Interfaces:
Usable, java.lang.Cloneable
public class PdfPopUpAnnot
extends PdfAnnot

This class represents a popup annotation. A popup annotation is actually the popup window of another annotation and hence cannot exist independently. It can be associated with another markup annotation using the annotation's setPopup() method.
